{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"ee75751b18","title":"中共中央、国务院、中央军委、中央文革小组关于大、中、小学校复课闹革命的通知","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"937dc3f635","index":0,"year":1967,"month":10,"day":14,"articleId":"ee75751b18","article":{}}],"tags":[{"name":"教育和教育革命","id":"299424f798","type":"主题"},{"name":"指示","id":"2d13338754","type":"文稿类型"},{"name":"红卫兵运动","id":"3be4d5766f","type":"主题"},{"name":"中共中央、国务院、中央军委、中央文革联发","id":"cbee4acb80","type":"发行机构"},{"name":"中央文件","id":"ef6e778547","type":"文稿大类"},{"name":"中央文革","id":"ef71f03227","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"wenku","name":"中国文化大革命文库（第一版）","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":"","articles":[],"comments":[],"contents":[],"pages":[]}],"authors":[]},"publication_details":{"wenku":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"7cda5e2a8b","type":"title","text":"中共中央、国务院、中央军委、中央文革小组关于大、中、小学校复课闹革命的通知","index":0,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"ee75751b18","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"d2c4e8e9d5","type":"paragraph","text":"各省、市、自治区革命委员会（筹备小组）、军管会，各大军区、省军区并转各群众组织：","index":1,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"ee75751b18","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"a12dda6fbf","type":"paragraph","text":"（一）全国各地大学、中学、小学一律立即开学。","index":2,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"ee75751b18","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"b0c0270635","type":"paragraph","text":"（二）各学校都必须认真执行毛主席关于斗私、批修的指示。","index":3,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"ee75751b18","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"368a503f5f","type":"paragraph","text":"（三）一切大中小学校一边进行教学，一边进行改革。在教学的实践中，贯彻实行毛主席的教育革命思想，逐步提出教学制度和教学内容的革命方案。","index":4,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"ee75751b18","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"f714a6d8a5","type":"paragraph","text":"（四）各学校应该遵照毛主席一九六七年三月七日的指示，要在革命的原则下，按照教学的班、级、系的系统，实现革命的大联合，建立革命三结合的领导班子。","index":5,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"ee75751b18","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"d30603c382","type":"paragraph","text":"（五）各学校的教师和干部，大多数是好的或比较好的。除了地、富、反、坏、右分子以外，有些人过去犯了错误，只要他们能够认识错误，改正错误，就应该让他们站出来工作。","index":6,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"ee75751b18","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"5e8401d235","type":"paragraph","text":"（六）各大中小学校都要立即积极筹备招生的事宜。","index":7,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"ee75751b18","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"43a23435a9","type":"paragraph","text":"（此件在各学校内张贴）","index":8,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"ee75751b18","publication":{},"article":{}}],"page":{"start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}